org.dejava.component.test.runner

Class JUnitParametricRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • BlockJUnit4ClassRunner
      • org.dejava.component.test.runner.JUnitParametricRunner

  • public class JUnitParametricRunner
extends BlockJUnit4ClassRunner
    JUnit runner that injects test data into tests. It runs the same test multiple times (if multiple data is given). It uses a custom annotation named ParametricTest to decide how test data will be retrieved. It also runs regular JUnit test annotated with @Test. In this cases, there is no data injection.
